"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-new-zealand-coach-claims-alex-yee-weaknesses-epic-olympic-triathlon-win-21334492\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Alex Yee won Olympic gold for Team GB in the men's triathlon with an epic comeback to beat New Zealand's Hayden Wilde.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7001312741289416, \"rank\": 0.4254451537597143, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 112, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee was trailing Wilde by 14 seconds at the start of the last lap and was being pursued hard by France's duo of Pierre Le Corre andLeoBergere.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9859425082068913, \"rank\": 0.014248817806971554, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 232, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Le_Corre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre Le Corre\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Le_Corre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Le_Corre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as Bergere pushed to close the 15-second ga on Yee, the Brit produced a late surge of his own to hunt down Wilde and overtake him in the final few hundred metres.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\", \"score\": 0.8773989922475945, \"rank\": 0.13934063533090812, \"text\": \"ga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning silver in the triathlon in Tokyo, Yee has now gone one step better with his gold medal inParisand was immediately congratulated by Wilde as they shared a hug by the finish line.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9847854454362823, \"rank\": 0.015445428517264277, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after winning his silver medal, Wilde gave a special mention to his New Zealand teammate, Dylan McCullough, who finished 19th but was part of the lead group during the cycling before he dropped back to create a slipstream for Wilde to catch up before the 10km run.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 666, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7001312741289416, \"rank\": 0.4254451537597143, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999994801575199, \"rank\": 5.046616383257221e-07, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}, {\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just want to, first off, say a massive thank you to Dylan McCullough.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999994801575199, \"rank\": 5.046616383257221e-07, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it wasn't for him coming back, I would not have done that,' Wilde told Sky.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999065633718501, \"rank\": 7.141534396116254e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He saved me a lot of energy on the bike.'\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde also said he was 'stoked' to see Yee win gold.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Just a great race overall.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I missed out on the end, but we recover now and try to get another medal,' Wilde said.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I looked back and there was a gap and he looked composed.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was hot, so that might have been an effect but I gave it everything, and I am stoked for Alex as well.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9919903135917683, \"rank\": 0.00797798301339472, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Just to have an even race, no penalties, just a pure, good foot race, and it was exciting.'\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, New Zealand coach, Craig Kirkwood, admitted after the race that his team were 'pretty confident' that Wilde could beat Yee.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7001312741289416, \"rank\": 0.4254451537597143, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Kirkwood\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Craig Kirkwood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Kirkwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Kirkwood\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Alex has definitely got weaknesses, so we tried to exploit those,' Kirkwood told RNZ.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9919903135917683, \"rank\": 0.00797798301339472, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirkwood_Formation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.340225221146787e-12, \"text\": \"Kirkwood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirkwood_Formation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirkwood_Formation\"}, {\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I thought he'd got [it] right today but just unlucky to not hold on.'\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked how he found the energy for the late surge to overtake Wilde, Yee said: 'I do not even know.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1883, \"end\": 1888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in quite a bad place to be fair.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was going through a really bad patch.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me, I rode that wave and just said one more try and let us see if I can do it.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not give up.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Almost two laps in I thought silver was on the cards.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I owed it to myself to give myself one last chance and with about 2k to go I thought I'd give it everything I had.'\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic triathlete throws up after swimming in filthy River Seine  ArrowMORE:North Korea and South Korea athletes pose for historic Olympics selfie  ArrowMORE:What Olympic medal winners get in the box during victory ceremony  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"score\": 0.8434355257791627, \"rank\": 0.18562599531335544, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9396727300384515, \"rank\": 0.04362805111022233, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPT